description: This file declares the interface for the Query Interface Object in the ANSC framework, including functions to add, delete, and query interface objects by name.

methods.name: AnscQioAddIf
methods.description: Adds a new interface with the specified name and handle to the object.

methods.name: AnscQioDelIf
methods.description: Deletes the interface with the specified name from the object.

methods.name: AnscQioQueryIf
methods.description: Retrieves the handle of the interface with the specified name.
